{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it told its story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could see what they projected.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he-- that was the minutes of this meeting, which lasted, I suppose, a couple of hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they had a nice whisky, in a lovely villa, in a lovely lake in Berlin area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went there afterwards-- it's now a Holocaust Memorial, I believe-- a-- one of many.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they-- he told them, all of these people that you think would find it horrifying, you know, 18-20 people, to go back and tell their agencies-- this is the minutes of the meeting, 15 pages long-- how it was going to be done.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The people were going to be brought over to-- to the east.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They thought it was better outside Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there they were to be brought to camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And those that were-- as they arrived, since they would be hard to feed them and so forth-- though they should be sorted out by very good physicians which ones could still do some good work, and quickly sorted.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the others right away-- they just disburdened themselves of the others, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was almost unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And these minutes were distributed in 47 different copies to all the different agencies for their records in their different regions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we found one copy-- one of the girls who will come to this reunion-- an English girl at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She married an American and lives near Philadelphia now-- Betty Richardson-- I guess-- I don't know what her married name is Nuk-- I think it might be N-U-K.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But she's here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You could even find her and see how it was to find that document.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She was in Berlin, the outpost Berlin, going through some of the agency files-- the German agency files-- and she found this.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
